### Whats now implemented (all plan todos completed)

- **SOL enabled end-to-end**: backend `ASSETS`, WS symbol maps + backup filters, funding map, dataset/historical builders, UI asset lists, per-asset controls, and the GOAT preset `ASSET_CONTROLS` now cover **BTC/ETH/XRP/SOL**.
